@startuml
title Deployment Diagram

skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam shadowing false

actor "User" as User
actor "Mobile Device" as Mobile

frame "Host Machine" {
  database "rsa-keys volume" as Keys
  node "rsa-server container" as ServerContainer {
    component "Flask RSA Server\nport 5000" as Server
  }
  node "rsa-client container" as ClientContainer {
    component "Client Demo" as Client
  }
}

User --> Server : HTTP (localhost:5000)
Mobile --> Server : HTTP (host_ip:5000)
ClientContainer --> ServerContainer : Docker bridge network
ServerContainer .. Keys : mounts

note bottom of Server
The server exposes the API on port 5000 and
reads/writes its RSA keypair into the mounted
volume.  The client connects to the server via
the Docker network when running in Compose.
end note

@enduml